      "text": "Whatever one may think about this theoretical prescription in view of long noviciates, probationary periods, possibilities of resignation or voluntariness of vows, it in no case captures the self-description of such systems and is probably not able to explain the peculiar circumstance that religious orders after their charismatic foundation typically oscillate between decay and revitalization."
